{"type":"message","id":"e9d0d448","parentId":"a2d34743","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:33:08.787Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-04-02 20:33 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下4个道简网络相关行业的最新动态（2026年3-4月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防/弱电工程\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n请搜索最新资讯，整理3-5条关键信息，每条信息包含：\n- 标题\n- 核心内容摘要（2-3句话）\n- 与道简网络业务的关联度（高/中/低）\n\n输出格式为Markdown，保存路径：/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1775133188784}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f29c8c8","parentId":"e9d0d448","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:33:19.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me search for the latest industry news for 道简网络's four core business areas: enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security/low-voltage engineering, network system integration, and IT operations services. I'll search for information from March-April 2026.","thinkingSignature":"9f6623250bebfada673f46862177fece0d73ac21582229f4e41a46f34fbbf4c7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l6o2h7w0niv6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":88,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42153,"totalTokens":42358,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.00010559999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00505836,"total":0.005199059999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775133188785}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c659797","parentId":"5f29c8c8","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:33:19.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l6o2h7w0niv6_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775133199742}}
{"type":"message","id":"75990472","parentId":"4c659797","timestamp":"2026-04-02T12:33:25.296Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest industry news in the four areas. I'll run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"9c5e4c53879747944f3707b652aa3aa7a2bdb2ef5ac3fbf8bad7f63e1f4ccab2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ptsvja20mf69_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 最新政策 趋势\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ptsvja20mf69_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 2026年3月 最新动态\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ptsvja20mf69_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 2026年 最新技术趋势\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ptsvja20mf69_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 2026年 最新发展 AIOps\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":902,"output":253,"cacheRead":41971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43126,"cost":{"input":0.00027059999999999996,"output":0.0003036,"cacheRead":0.0012591299999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018333299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775133199745}}
